column2: Following a hard fought victory by the Imperium to repel the voracious hordes of man-eating giantesses led by the notoriously evil and cheeky Darth Reus in the destructive Vore Wars that engulfed the entire British Isles, the Imperium is once again faced with a looming threat from its enemies. While the entirety of the isles exhausted its resources and strength to defeat Darth Reus and his armies, the cunning master ruseman droid NC-64 gears up his numberless droid armies for a crusade to conquer the entire British Isles. Already, numerous states have fallen under the seemingly limitless goons of NC-64 and his newly declared Spam Empire and once again, the Imperium is on the verge of crushing defeat, desperate for any kind of help...
